        Returns the enum constant of this type with the specified name. The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an enum constant in this type. (Extraneous whitespace characters are not permitted.)(返回具有指定名称的此类型的enum常数。该字符串必须与用于声明此类型的enum常数的标识符完全匹配。（不允许使用外部空白字符。）)
